%% x-story-manager: Story Manager
%% Universal Story operations (create/replan) with automatic Epic decomposition
%% Decompose-First Pattern: Build IDEAL plan → Check existing → Create or Replan

graph TD
    Start([Start: Story Manager]) --> Phase1[Phase 1: Discovery<br/>Team ID auto-discovery<br/>Parse Epic ID from request<br/>Load Epic description]

    Phase1 --> Phase2[Phase 2: Extract from Epic<br/>Q1-Q6: Parse Epic structure<br/>Persona, capability, value, AC, app type]

    Phase2 --> Phase3{Phase 3: Check<br/>Missing Info?}
    Phase3 -->|Some gaps| GatherMissing[Gather Missing Information<br/>Ask user for unanswered questions]
    Phase3 -->|All found| Phase4
    GatherMissing --> Phase4

    Phase4[Phase 4: Build IDEAL Story Plan ALWAYS<br/>Analyze Epic Scope<br/>Determine optimal count 5-10<br/>Build IDEAL plan in mind]

    Phase4 --> Phase5{Phase 5: Check<br/>Existing Stories?}

    Phase5 -->|Count = 0| CreateMode[CREATE MODE<br/>No existing Stories]
    Phase5 -->|Count ≥ 1| ReplanMode[REPLAN MODE<br/>Compare ideal vs existing]

    CreateMode --> Generate[Generate Story documents<br/>8 sections: Statement/Context/AC/Test/Tasks/Tech/DoD<br/>from IDEAL plan]
    Generate --> ShowCreate[Show preview:<br/>5-10 Stories to create<br/>Dependency-ordered]
    ShowCreate --> ConfirmCreate{User<br/>confirms?}
    ConfirmCreate -->|No| Phase4
    ConfirmCreate -->|Yes| ExecuteCreate[Create all Stories in Linear<br/>Update kanban_board.md]
    ExecuteCreate --> End([End: Summary])

    ReplanMode --> LoadExisting[Load existing Story descriptions<br/>Full 8 sections each<br/>Note current status]
    LoadExisting --> Compare[Compare IDEAL plan vs existing<br/>Fuzzy match by goal]
    Compare --> Categorize[Categorize operations:<br/>KEEP UPDATE OBSOLETE CREATE]
    Categorize --> ShowReplan[Show operations summary + diffs<br/>KEEP: no changes<br/>UPDATE: AC/Tech changed<br/>OBSOLETE: Cancel state=Canceled<br/>CREATE: new Stories needed]
    ShowReplan --> ConfirmReplan{User<br/>confirms?}
    ConfirmReplan -->|No| Phase4
    ConfirmReplan -->|Yes| ExecuteReplan[Execute operations:<br/>Keep/Update/Cancel/Create in Linear]
    ExecuteReplan --> UpdateKanban[Update kanban_board.md<br/>Remove Canceled Stories<br/>Add new Stories]
    UpdateKanban --> End

    %% Styling
    classDef discovery fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1976D2,stroke-width:2px
    classDef processing fill:#FFF9C4,stroke:#F57C00,stroke-width:2px
    classDef decision fill:#FFE0B2,stroke:#E64A19,stroke-width:2px
    classDef action fill:#C8E6C9,stroke:#388E3C,stroke-width:2px

    class Phase1,Phase2,LoadExisting discovery
    class CreateMode,ReplanMode,Generate,Compare,Categorize,GatherMissing,Phase4 processing
    class Phase3,Phase5,ConfirmCreate,ConfirmReplan decision
    class ExecuteCreate,ExecuteReplan,UpdateKanban,End action
